S.FORM: Petro Poroshenko I 1965 a miheca saka 9 folad saka 26 a romi'ad masofoc ci Petro Poroshenko, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Ukraine anini i ci Petro Poroshenko, patirengan a romi'ad i 2014 a miheca saka 6 folad saka 7 a romi'ad. His presidential term ended on 20 May 2019.
